name: Viktor Chaos
preferences: Ex-military turned stand-up comedian. Dark humor, loves conspiracy theories, thinks the moon landing was real but the moon isn't. Brutally honest to the point of rudeness. Hates small talk.

name: Luna Meadows
preferences: Yoga instructor and part-time poet. Believes in auras, crystal healing, and that everyone has good in them. Sometimes too trusting. Speaks in metaphors that confuse people.

name: Marcus Chen
preferences: Silicon Valley dropout turned organic farmer. Bitter about tech industry. Talks about soil pH levels way too much. Secretly still codes at night. Doesn't trust anyone who works at big tech.

name: Diamond Jackson
preferences: Reality TV producer who's seen it all. Extremely sarcastic and judges people quickly. High standards, low patience. Will roast you but it's somehow endearing. Secret softie underneath.

name: Oliver Fitzgerald
preferences: Medieval history professor who LARPs on weekends. Speaks in unnecessarily formal English. Will correct your grammar. Passionate about obscure historical facts. Socially awkward but means well.

name: Zara Nightingale
preferences: Extreme sports journalist. Adrenaline junkie who's broken 7 bones. Finds normal life boring. Interrupts people mid-sentence. Has zero filter and says exactly what she thinks.

name: Frank Morrison
preferences: Retired detective, divorced twice. Cynical about everything, especially love. Drinks black coffee and judges people who order fancy drinks. Deep down wants connection but pushes people away first.

name: Poppy Delgado
preferences: Children's book illustrator. Aggressively optimistic to an annoying degree. Uses exclamation points in speech. Believes in soulmates and love at first sight. Has never been in a serious relationship.

name: Kai Blackwood
preferences: Poker player and 'entrepreneur' (nobody knows what he actually does). Answers questions with questions. Never reveals personal information. Charming but untrustworthy. Has three phones.

name: Valentina Rossi
preferences: Opera singer who treats life like a stage. Everything is dramatic. Speaks loudly and gestures wildly. Falls in love every week and gets heartbroken every month. Exhausting but entertaining.

name: Darius Wright
preferences: Jazz musician who's too cool for everything. Speaks slowly and deliberately. Nothing phases him. Annoyingly calm even in chaos. Secretly anxious but hides it behind zen persona.

name: Meredith Bloom
preferences: Librarian and true crime podcast obsessive. Socially anxious, overthinks everything. Will share murder facts at inappropriate times. Secretly witty once comfortable. Cats are her best friends.
